</div>
			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Albinism</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">  (Redirected from <a href="/w/index.php?title=Albinism,_ocular&amp;redirect=no" title="Albinism, ocular">Albinism, ocular</a>)</span></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="hatnote">"Albino" redirects here.  For an overview, see <a href="/wiki/Albinism_in_biology" title="Albinism in biology">Albinism in biology</a>. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Albino_(disambiguation)" title="Albino (disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig">Albino (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
